        "MessageTW": "我正打算刪掉，怎麼了嗎？",
        "MessageEN": "I was just about to erase it. Why?"
    },
    {
        "MessageId": 101290230,
        "Flag": 2,
        "Type": 3,
        "NextId": 101290240,
        "MessageType": "Text",
        "ImagePath": "",
        "MessageJP": "消さないでおく？",
